reviewText: Funny series, but wouldnt have bought the entire set if Id remembered Phil Hartman died and was replaced with Jon Lovitz.  We stopped midway through the last season.
It's one of those must have series, especially now after JRE#82. Check it out.
Great series.  Still watching.  Packaging is perfect.  Price is very good.
I should not have to tell you how great this show is. Fantastic.
